---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`Équipement Pickleball | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Guide d'équipement pickleball : raquettes, balles, filets et accessoires testés et comparés." />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900">
    <Header />
    <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
      <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Équipement' }]} />
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Guide Équipement Pickleball</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-10 max-w-2xl">
        Retrouvez notre sélection des meilleurs équipements de pickleball, testés et comparés.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-center">🏓</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-center">Raquettes (Paddles)</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">De la raquette débutant à la raquette compétition, trouvez celle qui vous correspond.</p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">Selkirk Power Air</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">199 &euro;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">JOOLA Ben Johns</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">179 &euro;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">Head Radical Tour</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">149 &euro;</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-center">👟</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-center">Chaussures</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">Les chaussures adaptées au pickleball pour un bon maintien et une adhérence optimale.</p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">Nike Court Air Zoom</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">119 &euro;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">ASICS Gel-Renma</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">89 &euro;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">K-Swiss Express Light</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">79 &euro;</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4 text-center">🎾</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-center">Balles & Filets</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-4">Tout le matériel pour jouer au pickleball, en intérieur comme en extérieur.</p>
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">Franklin X-40 (x12)</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">24 &euro;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">Dura Fast 40 (x12)</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">29 &euro;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center p-3 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl">
              <span class="font-medium text-sm">Filet portable réglable</span>
              <span class="text-primary-700 font-bold text-sm">89 &euro;</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 p-5 bg-primary-50 rounded-2xl border border-primary-200 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-primary-800">
          En tant que Partenaire Amazon, nous réalisons un bénéfice sur les achats remplissant les conditions requises.
          Les prix affichés sont indicatifs et peuvent varier.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
